<h4 class='h12 talk-link__speaker'>Clint Smith</h4>
<h4 class='h9 m5'>
<a class='' href='http://www.ted.com/talks/2240?language=en' lang='en'>
How to raise a black son in America
</a>
</h4>
<div class='meta'>
<span class='meta__item'>
Posted
<span class='meta__val'>
