<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='282857' id='t-282857'>where the value of someone's life</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='284474' id='t-284474'>isn't determined by anything other 
than the fact that they had lungs,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='288273' id='t-288273'>a place where every single 
